Purchase Power By Ethnicity(Language)¶

In [88]:
lp=pd.DataFrame(df1.groupby(['Language'])['Purchase Price'].sum())
lp.reset_index(inplace=True)
plt.figure(figsize=(10,10))
plt.pie(x=lp['Purchase Price'],autopct='%1.0f%%',labels=lp.Language,textprops={'fontsize':20})
centre_circle=plt.Circle((0,0),0.5,color='black',fc='white',linewidth=0)
fig=plt.gcf()
fig.gca().add_artist(centre_circle)
plt.axis('equal')
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

f=amfr-pmfr
